{"tid":2455253,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［走資］抽走MPF另類方法","createTime":"2021-03-21T03:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T06:36:09.000Z","uid":83910,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b39da0501e4be20b10487c6d76faaf2642be9707","tid":2455253,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"諗到一個可以keep住抽走MPF嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n假設你MPF有50萬係保本基金<br />\n當升市或者市場高位果陣<br />\n你就買入北美股票基金<br />\n<br />\n另一方面<br />\n你就將你同等價值既VOO沽出（假設你持有）<br />\n<br />\n當個市跌返果陣<br />\n你就轉MPF去返保本<br />\n再買入VOO<br />\n<br />\n不斷重複 直至輸哂MPF去自己股票戶口<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得有無破綻？"},{"pid":"25f4c786d152cc8b26de0d900a688f287299129e","tid":2455253,"uid":262761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"如果股票戶口啲錢輸返入MPF點搞"},{"pid":"d13a83707088f056fa6d97183c6941070fdbaa79","tid":2455253,"uid":18795,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e179b3540494910c41b406da6a503edc40a754","tid":2455253,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25f4c786d152cc8b26de0d900a688f287299129e","tid":2455253,"uid":262761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"如果股票戶口啲錢輸返入MPF點搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"月供咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a2a7ec75430b86fdfb8f143053835a2be99470","tid":2455253,"uid":159876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"結果係，mpf 賺大錢，銀行戶口就蝕錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後諗都唔知一開始屌mpf 做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4142473cf7bb17fe385560f592d9b3cb2960c4a","tid":2455253,"uid":20473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T05:45:56.000Z","msg":"話自己搬去大灣區拎錢走"},{"pid":"9573